snippet: Arsenal and Manchester United played to a dour 0-0 draw that frustrated both teams, while Liverpool snatched a last-minute 3-2 victory at Fulham to return to the Premier League title race.
abstract: Arsenal and Manchester United play to frustrating 0-0 draw as Liverpool beats Fulham 3-2, returning to the Premier League title race; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: Arsenal and Manchester United played to a dour 0-0 draw that frustrated both teams, while Liverpool snatched a last-minute 3-2 victory at Fulham to return to the Premier League title race.
